Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.39,0:00:18.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Ridget...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.74,0:00:20.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, Commodore?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.99,0:00:21.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Take this.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.40,0:00:33.12,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.36,0:00:38.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Take good care of the fleet.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.36,0:00:43.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Commodore Fairlock,\N Gargantia needs you!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.21,0:00:46.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I have faith in you.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.58,0:00:47.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't think...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.47,0:00:51.54,Default,,0,0,0,,You've grown so much...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.54,0:00:56.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I can hold my head high when\N{\alpha&HFF&}.{\r}I give my report to your father.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.36,0:00:57.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Commodore!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.94,0:01:20.43,Default,,0,0,0,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.38,0:01:25.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Commodore!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.26,0:01:36.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Earth coordinates confirmed.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.82,0:01:42.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Current Galactic Alliance \Nstandard coordinates confirmed.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.24,0:01:43.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.47,0:01:45.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Can we go back?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.20,0:01:48.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Returning would necessitate faster-than-light travel.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.45,0:01:50.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I am incapable of such actions.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.07,0:01:52.17,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.17,0:01:53.13,Default,,0,0,0,,What about the distress beacon?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.71,0:01:59.05,Default,,0,0,0,,The estimated time of arrival of the first signals sent out upon crash-landing on Earth
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.05,0:02:03.93,Default,,0,0,0,,is 6582 years, 16 hours,\N and 20 minutes.{BOOM HEADSHOT}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.43,0:02:06.68,Default,,0,0,0,,That... can't be...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.68,0:02:10.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Returning to the fleet is\N{\alpha&HFF&}.{\r}realistically unfeasible.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.62,0:02:13.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't go back...
