Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.73,0:03:55.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Ridget?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.85,0:03:56.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you serious?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.99,0:03:58.54,Default,,0,0,0,,That little girl?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.54,0:04:01.05,Default,,0,0,0,,The Commodore himself appointed her.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.85,0:04:04.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I should just join Flange instead.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.81,0:04:06.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Ship commanders!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.93,0:04:08.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm glad you're all here.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.89,0:04:12.69,Default,,0,0,0,,We need to discuss Flange's request to split off from the fleet.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.69,0:04:13.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.95,0:04:15.50,Default,,0,0,0,,This isn't the time for that!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.50,0:04:17.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Commodore Fairlock's\N{\alpha&HFF&}.{\r}funeral is about to begin.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.90,0:04:20.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I know, but still—
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.13,0:04:22.45,Default,,0,0,0,,He thought of you as his own daughter.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.45,0:04:24.98,Default,,0,0,0,,How could missing his funeral even cross your mind?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.98,0:04:29.08,Default,,0,0,0,,He took you under his wing\N after Chevron died!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.88,0:04:33.62,Default,,0,0,0,,What are all of you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.20,0:04:36.33,Default,,0,0,0,,You should be heading towards the bow.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.67,0:04:37.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.88,0:04:38.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.06,0:04:48.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Opposition will always exist.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.29,0:04:52.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I know. I'll be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.85,0:04:54.98,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't go back?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.52,0:04:56.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.85,0:04:59.44,Default,,0,0,90,,I'm... sorry about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.11,0:05:01.19,Default,,0,0,90,,But you know,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.72,0:05:04.65,Default,,0,0,90,,if you can't go back, you'd\N{\alpha&HFF&}.{\r}better make up your mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.57,0:05:07.95,Default,,0,0,90,,You wanna kick some whalesquid ass, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.67,0:05:11.20,Default,,0,0,90,,Killing them is my duty.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.58,0:05:13.32,Default,,0,0,90,,So I guess you'd be interested
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.32,0:05:15.16,Default,,0,0,90,,in knowing the location of their nest?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.55,0:05:17.08,Default,,0,0,90,,There is a nest?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.08,0:05:19.14,Default,,0,0,90,,Calm down.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.14,0:05:21.96,Default,,0,0,90,,There's treasures down\N{\alpha&HFF&}.{\r}in the whalesquids' nest.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.62,0:05:23.51,Default,,0,0,0,,They're worth a lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.02,0:05:25.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Money does not interest me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.24,0:05:28.49,Default,,0,0,0,,You kill the whalesquids,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.49,0:05:30.54,Default,,0,0,0,,and I grab myself some treasure.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.97,0:05:31.64,Default,,0,0,0,,How about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.41,0:05:34.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I only care about killing them.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.80,0:05:36.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Looks like we've got ourselves a deal.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.61,0:05:43.11,Default,,0,0,0,,To release all the ships that want to leave, we'll have to unfasten thirty connectors.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.47,0:05:44.75,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a lot of work.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.75,0:05:46.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Get to it!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.45,0:05:51.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Flange, I beg you to reconsider.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.08,0:05:53.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I've already made my decision.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.54,0:05:58.17,Default,,0,0,0,,A huge fleet with weak leadership is the perfect target for pirates.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.66,0:05:59.97,Default,,0,0,0,,But still...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.97,0:06:02.17,Default,,0,0,0,,The heritage Pinion talked about
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.17,0:06:06.42,Default,,0,0,0,,might become the foundation of our future.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.42,0:06:11.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Besides, many people wish\N{\alpha&HFF&}.{\r}to leave with my ships.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.79,0:06:15.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Protecting the peaceful lives\N of those on my ships
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.77,0:06:17.94,Default,,0,0,0,,is my duty, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.00,0:06:22.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.98,0:06:24.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Anytime!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.42,0:06:26.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Melty!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.94,0:06:29.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Amy? Saya?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.16,0:06:32.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Melty, are you really leaving?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.16,0:06:32.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.83,0:06:35.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Why don't you let Flange's ships go, \Nand stay here with us?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.34,0:06:38.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't just leave my granddad alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.32,0:06:40.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.74,0:06:45.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Who would've thought my home ship \Nwould ever leave Gargantia?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.21,0:06:46.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I was the most surprised.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.25,0:06:51.26,Default,,0,0,0,,But who knows? It could be fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.26,0:06:54.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I might even meet a nice guy out there!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.67,0:06:55.79,Default,,0,0,0,,You wanna be Cinderella?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.79,0:06:57.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.02,0:06:59.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Not to mention that cutie's coming with us!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.57,0:07:00.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Ledo?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.04,0:07:03.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Pinion's been bragging about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.09,0:07:06.57,Default,,0,0,0,,"With that flying Yunboro on our side, \Nwe won't have to be afraid of any whalesquid!"
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.27,0:07:09.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.25,0:07:43.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I wanted you to succeed him, Krown.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.06,0:07:45.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't have much time left myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.90,0:07:48.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I must guide the next generation, while I'm still of this world.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.44,0:07:51.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Train her as best you can.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.12,0:07:54.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Commodore Fairlock,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.24,0:07:58.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I thank you for the journey we underwent together.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.25,0:08:03.37,Default,,0,0,0,,May the green waves be with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.24,0:09:03.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Not putting on your mourning gown?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.54,0:09:05.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Pinion!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.05,0:09:08.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you sign my parting request?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.26,0:09:10.37,Default,,0,0,0,,How many times do I have to repeat myself?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.21,0:09:15.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, show me why staying here \Nis worth my while.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.58,0:09:16.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I just—
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.73,0:09:20.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't stop people from leaving if you're\N{\alpha&HFF&}.{\r}not confident you can protect them.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.54,0:09:23.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Later.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.80,0:10:17.93,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.66,0:10:19.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Saya!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.53,0:10:22.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.47,0:10:25.43,Default,,0,0,0,,You're worrying about Ledo, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.43,0:10:27.56,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I'm not!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.56,0:10:31.52,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, you could go with him.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.64,0:10:35.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Just go with Melty on Mr. Flange's ships.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.89,0:10:38.07,Default,,0,0,0,,With Melty?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.49,0:10:40.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd miss you for sure,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.64,0:10:43.25,Default,,0,0,0,,but seeing you like this is even worse.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.25,0:10:44.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.11,0:10:46.74,Default,,0,0,0,,One look at your face, and you'd\N{\alpha&HFF&}.{\r}think the world was ending.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.64,0:10:50.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Although that's probably \N{\alpha&HFF&}.{\r}how it feels to you right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.29,0:10:55.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing even started between us...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.00,0:10:57.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Then—
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.68,0:10:58.59,Default,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.91,0:11:00.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I have to stay here.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.14,0:11:02.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you sure?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.16,0:11:04.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't leave Bevel behind.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.11,0:11:06.80,Default,,0,0,0,,He has to stay here with Dr. Ordum.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.80,0:11:09.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Besides, I couldn't live without Bevel.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.66,0:11:12.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.06,0:11:14.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.08,0:11:18.32,Default,,0,0,0,,That's a relief.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.30,0:11:23.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd miss you if you left, Amy!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.24,0:11:27.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks.
