Dialogue: 1,0:11:37.59,0:11:39.80,wtf TS?,,0,0,0,,{\fax-0.45\blur0.7\fsp-1\an7\c&H182428&\pos(25,516)\frz342.2}A long-time member of Mr. Fairlock's fleet
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.59,0:11:39.80,wtf TS?,,0,0,0,,{\fax-0.45\blur1.5\fsp-1\an7\c&H404547&\pos(25,516)\alpha&HD0&\frz342.2}A long-time member of Mr. Fairlock's fleet
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.54,0:11:45.22,Default,,0,0,0,,You look kinda troubled.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.79,0:11:47.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.34,0:11:49.18,Default,,0,0,0,,How about taking a break?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.74,0:11:52.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, what a great example {\i1}that{\i0} would set!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.53,0:11:56.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.82,0:11:58.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.67,0:12:02.73,Default,,0,0,0,,With the Commodore gone, I can't afford to look weak.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.73,0:12:05.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I know how hard you're working.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.70,0:12:06.90,Default,,0,0,0,,You're doing more than enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.58,0:12:09.79,Default,,0,0,0,,If I were, we wouldn't be in such a mess.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.20,0:12:13.25,Default,,0,0,0,,There's a difference between "enough" and "perfect."
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.90,0:12:17.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I went through a period\N{\alpha&HFF&}.{\r}like this too, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.42,0:12:21.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Back when my old man\N{\alpha&HFF&}.{\r}left me the business,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.61,0:12:25.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I tried to do everything myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.12,0:12:27.40,Default,,0,0,0,,One day, I found a huge catch.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.40,0:12:30.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I tried to show off all the skills I'd learned,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.27,0:12:32.25,Default,,0,0,0,,but I was swept away by the current,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.25,0:12:34.69,Default,,0,0,0,,and my Yunboro got stuck\N{\alpha&HFF&}.{\r}underneath my target.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.07,0:12:36.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought I was going to die there.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.15,0:12:41.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Pinion made fun of me, saying I couldn't keep track of my surroundings.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.06,0:12:45.36,Default,,0,0,0,,He said what I did was the same\N{\alpha&HFF&}.{\r}as not trusting my shipmates.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.98,0:12:49.93,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't have to do everything by yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.93,0:12:51.13,Default,,0,0,0,,So...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.13,0:12:53.29,Default,,0,0,0,,But Commodore Fairlock did just that!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.77,0:12:56.17,Default,,0,0,0,,That old man relied on you a lot!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.63,0:13:03.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Your job is figuring out who\N to entrust with what, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.11,0:13:05.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Entrust?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.14,0:13:09.05,Default,,0,0,0,,You use the stuff I salvage \N{\alpha&HFF&}.{\r}for the sake of the entire fleet.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.85,0:13:13.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd consider myself lucky if my ships were\N{\alpha&HFF&}.{\r}under the command of someone like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.50,0:13:16.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm home!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.62,0:13:18.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Welcome back.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.09,0:13:19.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry I'm late.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.63,0:13:21.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll start dinner right away!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.34,0:13:34.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, is it true that Ledo's leaving?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.99,0:13:36.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Where'd you hear that, Bevel?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.34,0:13:40.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I overheard the neighbors saying Pinion was talking about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.72,0:13:44.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. It's a shame, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.89,0:13:48.22,Default,,0,0,0,,We were just starting to get along, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.08,0:13:54.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder why he'd want to do something so dangerous.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.27,0:13:57.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Good question...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.94,0:14:01.26,Default,,0,0,0,,What an idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.17,0:14:03.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Amy...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.89,0:14:08.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Why doesn't he value his life?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.94,0:14:12.36,Default,,0,0,0,,It looked like he was having\N{\alpha&HFF&}...{\r}so much fun at the festival...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.36,0:14:13.79,Default,,0,0,0,,He was laughing!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.28,0:14:15.63,Default,,0,0,0,,But now,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.91,0:14:19.54,Default,,0,0,0,,he seems to be suffering even more than when we first met!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.54,0:14:23.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure the real Ledo is the one I saw at the festival!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.72,0:14:36.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{halftime}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.70,0:15:13.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Some chose to stay here, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.69,0:15:19.23,Default,,0,0,0,,How do you intend to deal with the boy?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.03,0:15:22.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll trust you with that decision.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.86,0:15:25.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Trust...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.76,0:15:41.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Bevel?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.17,0:15:43.72,Default,,0,0,0,,You're leaving?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.58,0:15:46.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.63,0:15:54.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you have to?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.65,0:15:57.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.26,0:16:01.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that really what you want to do, Ledo?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.82,0:16:03.73,Default,,0,0,0,,It's for the sake of mankind.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.73,0:16:05.30,Default,,0,0,0,,And Amy's as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.30,0:16:08.12,Default,,0,0,0,,But she never asked you to do that!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.49,0:16:16.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I want you to have this.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.61,0:16:20.41,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.49,0:16:22.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't this important to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.58,0:16:27.40,Default,,0,0,0,,It was made by a child\N{\alpha&HFF&}.{\r}who looked just like I did.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.81,0:16:29.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Just like you?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.17,0:16:33.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Thinking back, he might\N{\alpha&HFF&}.{\r}have been my little brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.38,0:16:35.79,Default,,0,0,0,,But then...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.79,0:16:39.63,Default,,0,0,0,,In the Galactic Alliance, a child\N{\alpha&HFF&}.{\r}who cannot fight cannot survive.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.32,0:16:44.14,Default,,0,0,0,,The Hideauze constantly\N{\alpha&HFF&}.{\r}encroach on our territory.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.49,0:16:45.15,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.93,0:16:47.65,Default,,0,0,0,,The same goes for the Earthian Hideauze.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.65,0:16:50.40,Default,,0,0,0,,If they one day decide\N{\alpha&HFF&}.{\r}to expand their territory,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.40,0:16:52.61,Default,,0,0,0,,a clash with mankind will be inevitable.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.10,0:16:54.38,Default,,0,0,0,,But the whalesquids—
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.09,0:16:56.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Those are Hideauze.{your face is hideauze}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.28,0:17:01.45,Default,,0,0,0,,If a similar situation to the Galactic Alliance arises here, you will not survive.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.38,0:17:06.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I do not want Amy to\N{\alpha&HFF&}.{\r}experience such a loss.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.16,0:17:09.01,Default,,0,0,0,,No! You're wrong, Ledo!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.01,0:17:10.59,Default,,0,0,0,,It won't come to that!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.59,0:17:12.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't want to make Amy sad.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.25,0:17:16.05,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why I'll destroy\N{\alpha&HFF&}.{\r}every last Hideauze.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.53,0:17:36.62,Default,,0,0,90,,Please wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.85,0:17:58.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I humbly apologize for my tardiness.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.60,0:18:19.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you... so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.08,0:18:51.98,Default,,0,0,0,,There is something we must all discuss.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.44,0:18:59.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Gargantia has been entrusted to me \N by Commodore Fairlock.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.03,0:19:06.87,Default,,0,0,0,,The future of the fleet occupied his thoughts until his very last moments.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.32,0:19:10.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to live up to his expectations.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.02,0:19:19.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to protect the Gargantia\N{\alpha&HFF&}.{\r}that the Commodore so loved.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.20,0:19:23.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to protect this fleet\N{\alpha&HFF&}.{\r}that we all live on.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.60,0:19:31.65,Default,,0,0,0,,By myself, I was helpless to even\N{\alpha&HFF&}.{\r}stop those who wanted to leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.98,0:19:34.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I... am powerless.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.65,0:19:43.52,Default,,0,0,0,,That is why I'm turning to you for help!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.52,0:19:48.84,Default,,0,0,0,,If you want to protect this fleet,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.84,0:19:52.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Gargantia, the stronghold harboring our lives,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.63,0:19:57.05,Default,,0,0,0,,then I implore you, please help me!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.02,0:20:21.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Who do you think we are?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.66,0:20:23.11,Default,,0,0,0,,We're veterans.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.48,0:20:24.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.45,0:20:27.08,Default,,0,0,0,,You can count on us to get things done!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.08,0:20:30.79,Default,,0,0,0,,No point in crying over the jerks who left!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.13,0:20:35.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Just stand in the middle,\N{\alpha&HFF&}.{\r}and rebuild the fleet around you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.17,0:20:37.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Ridget...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.65,0:20:38.80,Default,,0,0,0,,That'll do.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.56,0:20:47.94,Default,,0,0,0,,You all have my heartfelt gratitude.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.16,0:21:02.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Ledo...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.74,0:21:07.20,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing down there?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.20,0:21:08.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm about to leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.47,0:21:10.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.45,0:21:13.29,Default,,0,0,0,,So, Ledo...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.40,0:21:15.50,Default,,0,0,0,,You're really leaving?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.80,0:21:17.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.49,0:21:20.03,Default,,0,0,0,,But listen!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.03,0:21:21.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm just holding onto this for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.42,0:21:23.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Be sure to come back!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.56,0:21:26.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you for everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.37,0:21:30.32,Default,,0,0,0,,May the green waves be with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.92,0:21:59.36,Default,,0,0,0,,There's nothing you could've done.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.36,0:22:01.09,Default,,0,0,0,,They've already made up their minds.
